<https://www.gov.uk/government/people/matthew-pennycook> <http://ogp.me/ns#description> "Matthew Pennycook was appointed Minister of State at the Ministry of Housing, Communities and Local Government on 6 July 2024. He was elected as the MP for Greenwich and Woolwich in May 2015."@en .
